Body:
sd = SideDict()
assert sd.min_price() is None
sd[Price('100.0')] = 1
assert sd.min_price() == Price('100.0')
sd[Price('99.99')] = 1
assert sd.min_price() == Price('99.99')
sd[Price('100.001')] = 1
assert sd.min_price() == Price('99.99')
sd[Price('99.9999')] = 1
assert sd.min_price() == Price('99.99')
sd[Price('98.5')] = 1
assert sd.min_price() == Price('98.5')
sd[Price('98.4')] = 1
assert sd.min_price() == Price('98.4')
sd[Price('98.4')] = 2
assert sd.min_price() == Price('98.4')
sd[Price('98.4')] = 2
assert sd.min_price() == Price('98.4')
